<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>10244</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>22637</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>仆人领着柯普和哈姆走进王宫，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>22637</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>30334</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>国王向他们说明了公主的情况，两位聪明的哲学家听得非常认真。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>30334</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36665</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好了，现在请告诉我们，公主的情况要怎么解决？”国王问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36665</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44758</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>柯普先开口：“我知道了！公主的身体里进入了错误的灵魂。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44758</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50609</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>王后惊讶地眨了眨眼：“我不明白。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50609</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>55613</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我来解释一下，”柯普说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>55613</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65106</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“当婴儿出生时，他们必须要等待自己的灵魂，但这需要一些时间。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65106</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>70481</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我认为，是公主的身体里进入了错误的灵魂。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>70481</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>75414</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你在说什么火星语？”国王很生气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>75414</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80342</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“火星？不不不，陛下！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80342</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>88429</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>不是火星，我认为艾伦公主的灵魂来自水星。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>88429</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96218</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>不过不用担心，”柯普很快又说，“有一个非常简单的方法。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96218</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101539</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“呼！”国王笑了，“终于有好消息了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101539</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>107130</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “快请告诉我们！”王后说，“怎样才能治好公主？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107130</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111895</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“必须教她有关我们星球的一切。”柯普说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111895</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117219</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们的动物和植物。”他拍了拍下巴，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117219</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124759</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“当然！还有艺术和文学。这都需要时间，但是……”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124759</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128850</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不！不！不！”哈姆大声喊道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>128850</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136463</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他说的完全不对！现在轮到我了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136463</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141594</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我很清楚公主出了什么问题，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141594</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>150409</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>是她的身体——她的血液出了问题！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>150410</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154214</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “她的血液？”王后很惊讶。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154214</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>158015</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的。”哈姆点了点头，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>158015</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>166734</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“公主的血液流向了错误的方向，这就是她没有重量的原因。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>166734</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>171920</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>虽然不知道原因，但是想要治好她，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>171920</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>178274</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就必须先给她洗个热水澡，然后还需要准备……”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>178274</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>182019</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“够了！”国王非常生气，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>182019</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>187486</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们也许是最聪明的哲学家，但你们的想法实在是太可笑了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>187486</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>193050</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>王后点了点头：“希望你们能在王宫里住几天。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>193050</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>200210</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>仔细观察一下公主，然后再把你们的想法告诉我们。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>200210</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>205859</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>于是，两位哲学家住进了王宫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>205859</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>216213</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>好吧，大家觉得当哲学家们开始观察艾伦时，艾伦会做什么呢？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>216213</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>226495</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>——当然是哈哈大笑啦！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>